548
00:46:18,371 --> 00:46:24,412
[Horse gasping]

549
00:46:25,121 --> 00:46:26,996
[Sighs]

550
00:46:42,662 --> 00:46:44,037
Big Soldier:
Pretty good.

551
00:46:44,412 --> 00:46:47,329
Just a General, not a big deal.

552
00:46:48,329 --> 00:46:51,496
Maybe I'd capture their King later.

553
00:46:53,746 --> 00:46:55,912
Am I really a shame to Liang?

554
00:46:57,287 --> 00:46:59,412
Am I?

555
00:47:11,787 --> 00:47:13,329
Wei's General:
Come on.

556
