[Bird trilling]

571
00:48:11,120 --> 00:48:13,037
<i>Wei's General:
When I fulfill the conquest</i>

572
00:48:13,245 --> 00:48:16,412
<i>I'll start building my big boat.</i>

573
00:48:16,829 --> 00:48:20,329
