I'm a private.

587
00:49:45,870 --> 00:49:48,912
What's the difference?
You just kill.

588
00:49:51,079 --> 00:49:53,495
Big Soldier:
Hey, you're lost, right?

589
00:49:53,704 --> 00:49:57,454
You really think that when you get to
Shen Shu, everything will be all right?

590
00:50:01,245 --> 00:50:03,079
I'm a small potato.

591
00:50:06,079 --> 00:50:07,829
Wait, um...

592
00:50:08,579 --> 00:50:10,287
this map I have here,

593
00:50:10,829 --> 00:50:14,037
will get you to Shen Shu.

594
00:50:15,954 --> 00:50:19,120
