What's that?

606
00:51:44,537 --> 00:51:45,537
Patience.

607
00:51:45,703 --> 00:51:46,703
Wei's General:
Mister,

608
00:51:46,828 --> 00:51:48,703
please tell me which way is Wei.

609
00:51:48,995 --> 00:51:53,995
Student #1: That way.
Student #2: No, that way.

610
00:51:54,412 --> 00:51:57,953
<i>Wei has geographical advantages,
with Liang acting like a front shield,</i>

611
00:51:58,078 --> 00:52:00,620
<i>and Chu like a shield on the back.</i>

612
00:52:02,953 --> 00:52:05,370
<i>You can run, but you can't hide.</i>

