00:52:09,412 --> 00:52:11,620
[Horse whinnying]

614
00:52:16,287 --> 00:52:21,412
Man: Yeah!
[Crowd cheering]

615
00:52:30,662 --> 00:52:33,787
[Crowd cheering]

616
00:52:36,912 --> 00:52:38,453
Woman:
There.

617
00:52:43,912 --> 00:52:45,662
This is your new home now.

618
00:52:46,620 --> 00:52:48,245
I'm going home too.

619
00:52:52,870 --> 00:52:54,912
You live a good life.

620
00:52:58,870 --> 00:53:00,745
Pretty good.

