01:03:38,786 --> 01:03:43,619
[Man crying]

711
01:03:47,119 --> 01:03:48,869
[Man continues crying]

712
01:03:49,619 --> 01:03:51,494
Whoa!

713
01:03:52,827 --> 01:03:54,411
[Gasping]

714
01:03:55,244 --> 01:03:58,869
Aah!

715
