717
01:04:09,661 --> 01:04:12,786
This buffalo just lost his temper.

718
01:04:14,702 --> 01:04:18,661
Was this buffalo too power
or the wall was too weak?

719
01:04:18,827 --> 01:04:21,452
Not matter what, thank you.

720
01:04:21,744 --> 01:04:23,744
Pretty good. Pretty good.

721
01:04:24,994 --> 01:04:27,119
What's with your waist belt?

722
01:04:28,077 --> 01:04:29,327
My secret.

723
01:04:29,411 --> 01:04:33,077
Before we go separate ways,
I'll have a secret to tell.

724
01:04:33,577 --> 01:04:35,619
